Package: inat-rarity-explorer
Title: iNaturalist Rarity Explorer — Shiny App
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-04-01
Author: Garrett Craig <garrettgcraig@gmail.com>
Description: A Shiny dashboard that fetches a user's research-grade
    iNaturalist observations and ranks them by global observation count,
    surfacing the species they have observed that fewest others have recorded.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8

Imports:
    shiny (>= 1.8.0),
    shinydashboard (>= 0.7.2),
    shinyjs (>= 2.1.0),
    shinycssloaders (>= 1.0.0),
    httr (>= 1.4.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0),
    plotly (>= 4.10.0),
    DT (>= 0.28),
    dplyr (>= 1.1.0)

SystemRequirements: R (>= 4.2.0), internet access to api.inaturalist.org
URL: https://github.com/garrettgcraig/inat-rarity-explorer
BugReports: https://github.com/garrettgcraig/inat-rarity-explorer/issues
